    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Wikipedia &middot; <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Write-ahead_logging"><img src="/reading/wikipedia.svg" alt="wp" style="display:inline;height:1em;vertical-align:-0.1em;margin-right:0.2em;"/>Write-ahead logging</a> &middot; CC BY-SA 4.0</p>

